  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and cook for another minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the beef and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the Massaman paste and cook for 1-2 minutes, until fragrant.",
    "Pour in the coconut milk and add the fish sauce, sugar, salt, black pepper, cinnamon, clove, and cardamom.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 10-15 minutes, or until the meat is tender.",
    "Serve the curry over steamed jasmine rice.",
    "Garnish with toasted peanuts and fresh cilantro, if desired."
